1998 - 12-28
Major News Items in Leading Nigerian Newspapers
LAGOS , December 28 ( Xinhua ) -- Following are major news items in leading Nigerian newspapers Monday .
New Nigerian :
-- As Nigerians groan under the new pump price of petroleum products , the government may revisit the issue with a view to reducing current suffering of the masses .
The Guardian :
-- Residents of Sierra Leone 's capital Freetown burnt alive at the weekend two suspected rebel spies as citizens there are living under threat of a rebel assault .
Daily Times :
-- The Independent National Electoral Commission will begin screening of candidates for the governorship and state houses of assembly elections Monday .
